Some artists have sought ways to continue creating and sharing their work on the Internet as a replacement for traditional live performances, such as online and live concerts or online festivals created for artists to perform, broadcast and promote their work.
Online, many internet memes on the topic of coronavirus have spread as many favor humor and distraction over uncertainty.
